trans-unit.source: Specifies the properties that are in a <xref href="System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvilke egenskaper som er i en <xref href="System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A StylusPointDescription specifies which properties are associated with a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>.
trans-unit.target: En StylusPointDescription angir hvilke egenskaper som er knyttet til en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: For each property in a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>, the StylusPointDescription contains a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo> object which specifies constraints such as the minimum and maximum values of the property.
trans-unit.target: For hver egenskap i en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>, StylusPointDescription inneholder en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo>objekt som angir begrensninger for eksempel minimums- og maksimumsverdiene for egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointPropertyInfo> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.HasProperty%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.GetPropertyInfo%2A> methods to check for these properties in the StylusPointDescription.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.HasProperty%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.GetPropertyInfo%2A>metoder for å se etter disse egenskapene i StylusPointDescription.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.GetPropertyInfo%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointDescription.HasProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: All <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint> objects in a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> must share the same StylusPointDescription.
trans-unit.target: Alle <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>objekter i en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection>må ha samme StylusPointDescription.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>

trans-unit.source: If you try to add a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint> to a <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> that has a different StylusPointDescription, an exception will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du prøver å legge til en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>til en <xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection>med en annen StylusPointDescription, vil bli utløst et unntak.</xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPointCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Input.StylusPoint>
